Bhide is out in his living room, relaxing as he reads the newspaper. But soon his peace gets disrupted by Tapu Sena's constant noise and he tells them to keep quiet! Find out more by watching the episode.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #newyearcountdown #newyear2025 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Gurudev is a motivator, spiritual guru, an author, lecturer and a teacher of life. 
Aacharya Ratnasundersurishwarji Maharaj Saheb
Raj Pratibodhak Sarasvati Nandan Param Poojya Acharya Vijay Ratnasundersuriswarji is a renowned Jain saint. He was born on 5th January, 1948 at Depla (Near Palitana, Gujarat).
Being a religious guru, he wrote many visionary books for the sociol and cultural upliftment of the individual as well as society.

*Lakhi rakho aaras ni takti par*
 *Jher jyare nitri jai che*  these are the few of books which have brought about a sea change in the lives of many, across the globe.
He has written more than 450 books in gujarati.
Which are also been translated in English, Hindi, Marathi, Urdu, French in the hope of bringing positive change in all the people.

snippet.title: Live Meditation With Gurudev | World Meditation Day 21st Dec 2024
snippet.description:
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 on the occasion of World Meditation Day to meditate with Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar, this is going to be the most historic and largest meditation event. You don't want to miss out!

About #Gurudev - 
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 to celebrate World Meditation Day 
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and peaceful world. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.

Learn Sudarshan Kriya the world's most powerful breathing technique: https://aoliv.in/learnsudarshankriya

Do Like, Comment, Share & Subscribe to the channel!

Subscribe to Gurudev's Channel: 
https://youtube.com/srisri

üëÅÔ∏è‚Äçüó®Ô∏è Lyrics :

Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Aajya teri nazar utaru uljhi ye zulaf swaru
Ambran te aai apsara tere pe jaan bhi vaaru
Nadiyan or jheel ye jharne sab terte baat kare
Palke teri uthe swera jhukjya te raat kare
Sheeshe pe matna puche dekhle meri ankhya mein
Ladyu tere kan ke niche madam tikka kala main
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Deewana main tera tu meri mehbuba
Dhundhe ye meri nigahe tujhko hawao mein
Main toh kuch na mangu tu jo hasil hai
Haan bas marna chahu main toh teri bahon mein
Khulya tane asman dyu khushiyan ki chhatri taan dyu
Sapne tere pure kardyu na rakhu kade talya main
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Duniya tane sari dekhe
Tu meri taraf lkha
Chandan ki lakad hai tu bangya main sarp mkha
Aave har saal december chede ya dhund maney
Tha tha ke patke madam jaddya ki boond maney
Bille pe hath hai uska aadi na ant hai jiska
Mannat je puri hogi ladyu dive aalya main
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Episode 4275: Shaadi Ka Darr
--------------------------------------------------------
Sonu and Tapu find themselves in a panic when their families start looking for compatible life partners. Will they have the ability to devise a strategy, desperate to dodge arranged marriages?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
A special day calls for a special announcement üéÇ 
#Subedaar, new movie, coming soon

ABOUT SUBEDAAR
Set in the Indian heartland, the powerful masala action-drama follows Subedaar Arjun Maurya as he grapples with the challenges of leading a civilian life, navigates a strained relationship with his daughter and confronts societal dysfunction. Once a soldier who fought for the nation,
Subedaar must now battle enemies within to protect his home and family.

Directed by: Suresh Triveni
Produced by: Vikram Malhotra, Anil Kapoor, Suresh Triveni
Written by: Suresh Triveni, Prajwal Chandrashekar
An Opening Image Films and Anil Kapoor Film & Communication Network (AKFCN) Production

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Best School in the World | School Aaj Kal | Take A Break
snippet.description:
What would schools say if they dropped the facade and got real? Welcome to School Aaj Kal, a hilarious yet thought-provoking comedy sketch that imagines just that! üéìüí∏
In this video, we explore how schools today often focus more on profits than education, becoming money-churning machines rather than true centers of learning. From exorbitant fees and "mandatory" extracurriculars to endless add-ons like "smart classrooms" and overpriced uniforms, this sketch dives into the absurdities of modern-day schooling with a pinch of satire and a truckload of laughs.

Get ready to laugh, relate, and maybe even question the reality of today‚Äôs education system. Because sometimes, honesty is the funniest policy! üòÇ

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

A day at a Farmhouse in Hyderabad offers a perfect blend of nature, tranquility, and authentic experiences. The city,known for its bustling urban life, is also home to several peaceful farmhouses that provide an escape into nature. Spending a day in a Hyderabad farmhouse allows you to enjoy the fresh air, lush greenery, and the calm away from the noise of the city. Whether it's enjoying traditional food,engaging in fun outdoor activities, or simply relaxing in the serene environment, Hyderabad's farmhouse cater to all. It's ideal destination for those seeking a break from the fast-paced city life and wanting to experience rural charm.

A day in the Hyderabad farmhouse offers more than just a relaxing getaway-it's an opportunity to reconnect with nature and experience the beauty of rural life. From the moment you step in, you're greeted with the refreshing sights and sounds of greenery,making it a perfect escape from the hectic city. The farmhouse often offers outdoor activities like farming,nature walks, and even games for the whole family,making it an ideal spot for group outings. In addition to the peaceful environment, the food at these farmhouses is typically made with fresh,local ingredients,providing a true taste of the region's traditional cuisine. Whether you want to enjoy a peaceful day in the lap of nature or indulge in a little adventure,Hyderabad's farmhouses provide a variety of experiences that will leave you refreshed and rejuvenated. For anyone visiting the city, a day spent at a farmhouse is truly unforgettable and worth the time.
